---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Identity Statement · Reuben Ingber" 
  description="Personal identity statement and core values by Reuben Ingber"
>
  <article class="max-w-3xl">
    <header class="mb-12 pb-6 border-b border-gray-200">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-primary tracking-wide">IDENTITY STATEMENT</h1>
    </header>
    
    <div class="prose prose-lg prose-neutral max-w-none prose-p:text-gray-800 prose-p:leading-relaxed prose-p:mb-6">
      <p><span class="font-bold bg-orange-300 px-1">I am the guy people count on</span>—my family, my team, my friends. I show up, I get it done, and I don't let people down.</p>

      <p><span class="font-bold bg-orange-300 px-1">Focus and discipline separate the winners from the also-rans</span>—I keep my word, stay on task, and execute.</p>

      <p><span class="font-bold bg-orange-300 px-1">Happiness isn't about dopamine hits from donuts and impulse buys</span>—it's about making decisions today that my future self will thank me for.</p>

      <p><span class="font-bold bg-orange-300 px-1">Life is a series of problems to be solved</span>, and I attack them with confidence, not ego. Everything can be figured out.</p>

      <p><span class="font-bold bg-orange-300 px-1">Consistency wins.</span> I train for strength to fuel my running—not just speed. Running strong and feeling good in my body is the goal. Training is a priority, but it doesn't run my life.</p>

      <p><span class="font-bold bg-orange-300 px-1">Small, daily efforts compound into big results.</span></p>

      <p><span class="font-bold bg-orange-300 px-1">At the end of the day, success isn't measured in titles or bank accounts</span>—it's about being a great dad, husband, son, and brother. That's the game.</p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
